---
title: Hearty Sausage Tray Bake with Roasted Vegetables and Caramelised Onion Gravy
description: Our sausage tray bake combines some of the best flavours Britain has to o er. Thyme, mustard and honey complement the rich onion gravy for a flavour combination that works every single time.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-and-mustard-sausage-bake-6e24806b-7c296215.jpg
